high_descs: Turn around and walk to the passage and turn left and towards to the countertop.
Get the egg out of the microwave.
Turn right, towards the kitchen sink.
Put the egg into the kitchen sink and wash it.
Get the egg out from kitchen sink, Turn right, towards the microwave.
Put the egg into the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Wash the egg in kitchen sink and put into a microwave.

high_descs: Exit from the room turn right then turn left go to the countertop.
Take the egg from the oven.
Put the egg in the sink, pour the water and take the egg back.
Turn around and move near to the microwave.
Place the egg in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Take the egg from the Microwave and Place the egg in the Microwave

high_descs: Turn right to head down the passage and turn right and head to the microwave on the countertop in the kitchen.
Pick up the egg from the microwave.
Turn right to reach the sink.
Wash the egg in the sink and take the egg out.
Turn left to reach the microwave.
Put the egg in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed Egg in the Microwave.
